// Information About The Torrent

Q: What separates this from all the other Terraria torrents out there?
A: I have decompliled the game and edited the source code to do 2 things.
Remove all steam dependency. And moved the games save folder to the current directory. In doing so it allows the game to be played on ANY computer via flash drive or network. and even rewrite-able CD. All your saves are kept nice and tidy in the same directory as the application. I will start adding more features to the game itself. But as for right now this is all I have done.

Q: Can I play online?
A: Yes you can. Any server you can find! You can also host.
